flowchart TD
    A([Login attempt fails]) --> B{Identity exists and account countable?}
    B -- No --> C[Apply IP/fingerprint rate limiting only]
    C --> D[Return generic error]
    B -- Yes --> E{Failure type}
    E -- Wrong password --> F[Increment credential failure score]
    E -- Wrong MFA --> G[Increment challenge attempts and global score]
    E -- Disallowed IP --> H[Increment separately weighted IP score]
    F --> I{Weighted threshold reached?}
    G --> I
    H --> I
    I -- No --> D
    I -- Yes --> J[Lock account]
    J --> K[Increment securityVersion]
    K --> L[Revoke all sessions]
    L --> M[Notify/audit security event]
    M --> N([Admin unlock required by default])
